<h1><%=
  current_user.name.ends_with?("s") ? "#{current_user.name}'" : "#{current_user.name}'s"

%> Account</h1>

<%= info "Better page coming soon!" %>

<h2>Account Information</h2>
<table id="account-information">
  <tr>
    <td>Username</td>
    <td><%= current_user.login %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Email address</td>
    <td><%= current_user.email %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>PIN number</td>
    <td><%= current_user.pin_number %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2>What is this page for?</h2>

<p>This Manage Account page is mostly for features that we'll be rolling out in the near future. For the time being, it's just a way of viewing very basic information about your account.</p>

<p>Here are some of the things we're working on:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Public sandbox phone number:</strong> Use your cell phone to test your sandbox app!</li>
  <li><strong>Component sharing:</strong> Let this site aggregate from Github and display your Adhearsion applications and components!</li>
  <li><strong>Example sharing:</strong> Help contribute to the Adhearsion Examples page but submitting your own!</li>
  <li><strong>Change your password</strong> Ok, not so amazing but probably useful to someone eventually.</li>
</ul>
  